wiki.summary: “Moonwalking in Calabasas Remix” continues the braggadocios energy by DDG adding Blueface and them rapping about the rapper lifestyle with having one night stands with women and owning expensive items from clothing to cars. Blueface brings his classic comedy-bar filled verses to rap about having money but being cheap on dates and ordering Dior but forgetting after a one night stand. DDG and Blueface have been close since late 2019 when they did a venue together. This marks the first official collaboration between the two artists. Read more on Last.fm.

This marks the first official collaboration between the two artists. “Moonwalking in Calabasas (Remix)” was certified platinum by the RIAA on June 2, 2021. Read more on Last.fm.
